document_data.mainbody:
he Codsbay was a small part of the Sea of Moonshae located on the northern coast of the island of Gwynneth within the kingdom of Oman in the Moonshae Isles.
The bay was located along the Strait of Oman at the mouth of the Codsrun Creek were it emptied into the sea at the Codsbay Mire.
